    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1910-11-05T23:59:59-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1910-11-05T00:00:00-05:00" n="941"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d941">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 892.001/10.</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Minister of Foreign Affairs of
                            Siam</gloss> to the <gloss type="to">Secretary of State</gloss>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Bangkok</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1910-11-05">
                            <hi rend="italic">November 5, 1910</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>I have the honor to acknowledge receipt of your telegram of 5th instant. It gives
                    me pleasure to inform you that Hon. George Cornell Tarler will be cordially
                    received as special representative of the President of the United States at His
                    Majesty’s coronation.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Devawonges.</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
